dhcp-ip-addr.help: IP address of the monitoring DHCP request packet sent through the tunnel.
dhcp-ip-addr.name: dhcp-ip-addr

ping-interval.help: Interval between two tunnel monitoring echo packets (1 - 65535 sec, default = 1).
ping-interval.name: ping-interval

ping-number.help: Number of the tunnel monitoring echo packets (1 - 65535, default = 5).
ping-number.name: ping-number

return-packet-timeout.help: Window of time for the return packets from the tunnel's remote end (1 - 65535 sec, default = 160).
return-packet-timeout.name: return-packet-timeout

wag-ip.help: IP Address of the wireless access gateway.
wag-ip.name: wag-ip

wag-port.help: UDP port of the wireless access gateway.
wag-port.name: wag-port

results.help: Configure wireless access gateway (WAG) profiles used for tunnels on AP.
results.name: wag-profile
